AttributeList.Text: ================================================================================ TThis module evalute the diagnostic byte from the Siemens safety Functionblock FB 216 "F_FDBACK" and generates a feedback alarm in the standard program. A boolean output is available to inform the upper level that the alarm can be reset. This module generates also a word containing all necessary information for HMI Icon animation, and a word with all information for HMI safety module diagnostic screen. ================================================================================
